Package: docprinter
Architecture: all
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce, adduser, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DocPrinter HTTP service (Docker + systemd)
 Runs the DocPrinter container under systemd. Depends on a Docker engine
 package; pulls the configured image on configure. Host paths: config under
 /etc/docprinter, logs under /var/log/docprinter, runtime data under
 /var/lib/docprinter/runtime.
